text: Camisiidae is a family of oribatids in the order Oribatida. There are at least 3 genera and 70 described species in Camisiidae. ==Genera== * Austronothrus Hammer, 1966 * Camisia Heyden, 1826 * Heminothrus Berlese, 1913 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * Category:Acariformes
